{"view":"article","slug":"big-l2e","category":"CHS","subcategory":null,"topDir":"CHS","title":{"zh":"高阶L2E公式（后二棱）"},"content":{"zh":"<p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/big-l2e/zh/image2.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/big-l2e/zh/image4.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><strong>高阶L2E公式（后二棱）</strong></p><p><strong>[Flip] </strong>= <strong>U' R' U R' F R F', A: B = A B A'</strong>. 本表不包含与五阶类似和一些不太明显的情况。一般地，先做内侧L2E再做整个L2E。六阶可能存在棱特，O特，P特；七阶可能存在棱特。若六阶的棱特存在，则可以按以下方法消去O特。先忽略未还原棱继续还原直到三阶最后一组F2L或OLL，将它放在UF处。OLL阶段：若顶层共有偶数对的正向外翼，则做内棱特，反之做外棱特。最后一组F2L阶段：若顶层和空槽共有奇数对的正向外翼，则做内棱特，反之做外棱特。六色底玩家应选择未还原棱的两色之一的对色作为十字底色，例如若未还原棱为橙蓝棱，则选择红或绿底十字。白底玩家不能有未还原白棱，且应尽量选择未还原黄棱。注：外棱特 = 翻内棱；内棱特 = 翻内棱 = 外棱特 + P特。</p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/big-l2e/zh/image6.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/big-l2e/zh/image8.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/big-l2e/zh/image10.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/big-l2e/zh/image12.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><em>内棱特</em></p></td><td><p><em>外棱特</em></p></td><td><p><em>内棱特</em></p></td><td><p><em>外棱特</em></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"4\"><p><strong>六阶</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/big-l2e/zh/image14.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/big-l2e/zh/image16.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/big-l2e/zh/image18.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/big-l2e/zh/image20.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>3r': [Flip]</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>3L: [Flip]</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>3R' l: [Flip]</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>l: [Flip] 3R': [Flip]</strong></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><a id=\"_Hlk522920324\"></a><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/big-l2e/zh/image22.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>r U2 x r U2 (r U2' r' U2) l U2 (4r' U2' r U2) r' U2' r' </strong><em>(外棱特)</em></p><p><strong>3r U2 x (3r U2 3R U2) x' (3L' U2 3L U2) (3R' U2 3R U2) 3r' U2 3r' </strong><em>(内棱特)</em></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"6\"><p><strong>七阶</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><a id=\"_Hlk522908444\"></a><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/big-l2e/zh/image24.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/big-l2e/zh/image26.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/big-l2e/zh/image28.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/big-l2e/zh/image30.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"(3R2 F2 U2') (3R2 U2' F2) 3R2\">(3R2 F2 U2') (3R2 U2' F2) 3R2</span></p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"(U R U' B) (3R2 F2 U2') (3R2 U2' F2) 3R2\">(U R U' B) (3R2 F2 U2') (3R2 U2' F2) 3R2</span></p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"r U2 x r U2 (r U2' r' U2) l U2 (5r' U2' r U2) r' U2' r'\">r U2 x r U2 (r U2' r' U2) l U2 (5r' U2' r U2) r' U2' r'</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"3r U2 x 3r U2 (3r U2' 3r' U2) 3l U2 (4r' U2' 3r U2) 3r' U2' 3r'\">3r U2 x 3r U2 (3r U2' 3r' U2) 3l U2 (4r' U2' 3r U2) 3r' U2' 3r'</span></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\"><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/big-l2e/zh/image32.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/big-l2e/zh/image34.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/big-l2e/zh/image36.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\"><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"3r U2 x (3r U2 3R U2) x' (3L' U2 3L U2) (3R' U2 3R U2) (3r' U2 3r')\">3r U2 x (3r U2 3R U2) x' (3L' U2 3L U2) (3R' U2 3R U2) (3r' U2 3r')</span></p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"3R U2 3R U2 x U2 3R U2 x' 3L' U2 3L U2 3R2\">3R U2 3R U2 x U2 3R U2 x' 3L' U2 3L U2 3R2</span></p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"3R2' B2 3R' U2 3R' U2 x' U2 3R' U2 3R U2 3R' U2 3R2\">3R2' B2 3R' U2 3R' U2 x' U2 3R' U2 3R U2 3R' U2 3R2</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div>"},"algs":["(3R2 F2 U2') (3R2 U2' F2) 3R2","(U R U' B) (3R2 F2 U2') (3R2 U2' F2) 3R2","r U2 x r U2 (r U2' r' U2) l U2 (5r' U2' r U2) r' U2' r'","3r U2 x 3r U2 (3r U2' 3r' U2) 3l U2 (4r' U2' 3r U2) 3r' U2' 3r'","3r U2 x (3r U2 3R U2) x' (3L' U2 3L U2) (3R' U2 3R U2) (3r' U2 3r')","3R U2 3R U2 x U2 3R U2 x' 3L' U2 3L U2 3R2","3R2' B2 3R' U2 3R' U2 x' U2 3R' U2 3R U2 3R' U2 3R2"],"thumb":"/stats/tutorial/media/big-l2e/zh/image2.svg","warningCount":0,"hasImages":true,"hasTables":true}
